"title": "4552: wood",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4552",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Trunks and branches of trees used as raw material for various objects and as fuel for burning. Acacia wood was used extensively in the tabernacle and olive wood in the temple.</p>\n<h2>Various kinds of wood</h2>\n<h3>Acacia wood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:1\">EXO 27:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:10-Exod25:13\">EXO 25:10–25:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:23\">EXO 25:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:15-Exod26:17\">EXO 26:15–26:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:26-Exod26:27\">EXO 26:26–26:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod27:6\">EXO 27:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:1-Exod30:5\">EXO 30:1–30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:4-Exod35:7\">EXO 35:4–35:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:24\">EXO 35:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:1-Exod37:4\">EXO 37:1–37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod38:1\">EXO 38:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:1-Deut10:3\">DEU 10:1–10:3</a></p>\n<h3>Cedar wood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:48-Lev14:53\">LEV 14:48–14:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:1-Lev14:7\">LEV 14:1–14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num19:1-Num19:8\">NUM 19:1–19:8</a></p>\n<h3>Olive wood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:23\">1KI 6:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:31-1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:31–6:35</a></p>\n<h3>Cypress wood</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:3-Ezek27:6\">EZK 27:3–27:6</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Items made from wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:19\">EXO 7:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:29-Lev11:32\">LEV 11:29–11:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev15:11-Lev15:12\">LEV 15:11–15:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num31:19-Num31:20\">NUM 31:19–31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:16-Num35:18\">NUM 35:16–35:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:4\">NEH 8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:15\">ISA 10:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:13\">JER 28:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek15:2-Ezek15:3\">EZK 15:2–15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:22\">EZK 41:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:25\">EZK 41:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:20\">2TI 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Wooden idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:16-Deut29:18\">DEU 29:16–29:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:36\">DEU 28:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:64\">DEU 28:64</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:26\">JDG 6:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:18\">2KI 19:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:19\">ISA 37:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:18-Isa40:20\">ISA 40:18–40:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:13-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:13–44:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:20\">ISA 45:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:5\">ISA 48:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:26-Jer2:28\">JER 2:26–2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:9\">JER 3:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:6-Jer10:8\">JER 10:6–10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek20:32\">EZK 20:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:1-Dan5:4\">DAN 5:1–5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:23\">DAN 5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:12\">HOS 4:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:5-Hos10:6\">HOS 10:5–10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:19\">HAB 2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20\">REV 9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Carpentry</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:1-Exod31:5\">EXO 31:1–31:5</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:30-Exod35:33\">EXO 35:30–35:33</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Wood for burning sacrifices</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:34\">NEH 10:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:3-Gen22:13\">GEN 22:3–22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev1:3-Lev1:17\">LEV 1:3–1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev3:1-Lev3:5\">LEV 3:1–3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam6:14\">1SA 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:22-2Sam24:23\">2SA 24:22–24:23</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:23\">1CH 21:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:22-1Kgs18:24\">1KI 18:22–18:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:30-1Kgs18:38\">1KI 18:30–18:38</a></p>\n<h2>Wood as fuel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek24:3-Ezek24:5\">EZK 24:3–24:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov26:20-Prov26:21\">PRO 26:20–26:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:13-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:13–44:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek15:1-Ezek15:8\">EZK 15:1–15:8</a></p>\n<h2>Chopping and gathering wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:5\">DEU 19:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:32-Num15:36\">NUM 15:32–15:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:10-Deut29:11\">DEU 29:10–29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:3-Josh9:27\">JOS 9:3–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:1-2Kgs6:7\">2KI 6:1–6:7</a></p>\n<h2>Metaphorical references to wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:6\">ZEC 12:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job41:27\">JOB 41:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:12-Jer5:14\">JER 5:12–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Symbolic use of wood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:15-Ezek37:28\">EZK 37:15–37:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:23-Exod15:26\">EXO 15:23–15:26</a></p>",
